        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "refactor: internalize OpenClaw agent runtime",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- rename the former Pi agent runtime/package surfaces to OpenClaw-owned agent runtime names\n- internalize the runtime packages into core and wire the embedded OpenClaw runtime through the current plugin/runtime contracts\n- remove copied session-export HTML assets, package-manager install/update leftovers, runtime `.pi` auth discovery, and stale internal Pi naming\n- split modern agent runtime id helpers from deprecated Pi runtime-id compatibility; keep compatibility in explicit doctor/session/env/plugin-boundary helpers\n- keep deprecated plugin SDK compatibility only at named boundaries, including `resolveLegacyAgentAccessToken`\n- add the Pi third-party notice for incorporated code\n\n## Verification\n\nBehavior addressed: OpenClaw no longer has live core/runtime paths depending on Pi package names or `.pi` credential discovery; remaining Pi runtime-id compatibility is isolated in deprecated compat helpers for shipped config/session/env values and plugin SDK boundary compatibility.\nReal environment tested: local macOS checkout plus Linux Blacksmith Testbox through Crabbox.\nExact steps or command run after this patch: `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/aliases.test.ts src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/run/backend.test.ts src/agents/harness/selection.test.ts src/agents/harness/runtime-plugin.test.ts src/agents/openai-codex-routing.test.ts src/agents/runtime-plan/build.test.ts src/agents/command/cli-compaction.test.ts src/gateway/server-startup.test.ts src/gateway/server-startup-post-attach.test.ts`; `node scripts/run-tsgo.mjs -b tsconfig.projects.json`; `node scripts/run-oxlint.mjs <changed files>`; `git diff --check`; `/Users/steipete/Projects/agent-scripts/skills/autoreview/scripts/autoreview --mode local`; `node scripts/crabbox-wrapper.mjs run --provider blacksmith-testbox ... corepack pnpm check:changed`.\nEvidence after fix: targeted Vitest passed 13 files / 181 tests; local tsgo passed; targeted oxlint passed; `git diff --check` passed; autoreview clean; Testbox-through-Crabbox `tbx_01ksafhp87h8heqjsjwb7z9wgk` passed `pnpm check:changed` in Actions run https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/actions/runs/26333664224.\nObserved result after fix: `src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/runtime.ts` is gone; modern runtime-id helpers live in `src/agents/agent-runtime-id.ts`; deprecated Pi alias handling is quarantined in `src/agents/deprecated-agent-runtime-compat.ts`; plugin SDK `resolveEmbeddedAgentRuntime` remains exported.\nWhat was not tested: full Vitest suite and live provider usage calls.\n",
